eNCA's Silindelo Masikane is following this story. Courtesy #DStv403  JOHANNESBURG -Advocate Malesela Teffo has withdrawn as counsel in the Senzo Meyiwa murder trial due to alleged harassment from the state and court.  Advocate Malesela Teffo has withdrawn as counsel for accused one to four in the Senzo Meyiwa murder trial because of alleged harassment from state and court. Courtesy #DStv403 #eNCA  Teffo represents accused 1-4 in the trial. READ: EXCLUSIVE: In conversation with Advocate Malesela Teffo The Senzo Meyiwa murder matter returned to the North Gauteng High Court on Tuesday. The trial has been postponed until 02 August 2022.